subsection.text:

  Section 442 of the Homeland Security Act of 2002 (
  6 U.S.C. 252
) is amended to read as follows:

subparagraph.text:
civil enforcement of immigration laws, as such term is defined in 
                      paragraph (17) of section 101(a)
